title: Expanding Information by Utilizing Uncertain Data
text: > Blurbs > Expanding Information by Utilizing Uncertain Data Text Size: Expanding Information by Utilizing Uncertain Data https://www.onlinepublications.austroads.com.au/items/AP-T301-15 173321 Expanding Information by Utilizing Uncertain Data Austroads has released a report that details an exploratory use of a set of time series rutting data from a long-term pavement performance site in condition calculations. This report is available for no fee after logging on to the site.
